  <brief_title>Frequency of Hypoglycaemic Episodes During Treatment With Insulin Detemir in Well Controlled Subjects With Type 1 Diabetes</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomised, Open Label, Cross-over, Multi-centre, Multinational Trial Comparing the Frequency of Hypoglycaemic Episodes During Treatment With Insulin Detemir and NPH Insulin in Well Controlled Subjects With Type 1 Diabetes on a Basal-bolus Regimen</official_title>
